{"id":1205,"date":"2018-08-02T17:41:02","date_gmt":"2018-08-02T21:41:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=1205"},"modified":"2023-06-12T12:04:50","modified_gmt":"2023-06-12T16:04:50","slug":"manon-plante","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/manon-plante\/","title":{"rendered":"Manon Plante"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Manon Plante a \u00e9tudi\u00e9 en litt\u00e9rature \u00e0 l\u2019Universit\u00e9 de Montr\u00e9al. Elle s\u2019est fait happer par la po\u00e9sie fran\u00e7aise, singuli\u00e8rement par les \u0153uvres de Ren\u00e9 Char et de Jacques Roubaud, et par la po\u00e9sie qu\u00e9b\u00e9coise de Gaston Miron et de Gilles H\u00e9nault.<\/p>\n<p>Elle est aussi membre du comit\u00e9 de r\u00e9daction de la revue culturelle\u00a0<em>Spirale<\/em>. Convaincue que la litt\u00e9rature est un territoire o\u00f9 s\u2019entrecroisent la sensibilit\u00e9 et la pens\u00e9e, elle voudrait aider ses \u00e9tudiants et \u00e9tudiantes \u00e0 se frayer un vivant chemin vers les \u0153uvres litt\u00e9raires et vit de l\u2019espoir qu\u2019ils en seront saisis.<\/p>\n<p>Citation pr\u00e9f\u00e9r\u00e9e\u00a0:<\/p>\n<p>Le po\u00e8te, conservateur des infinis visages du vivant.<\/p>\n<p>Ren\u00e9 Char,\u00a0<em>Feuillets d\u2019Hypnos<\/em>, 1946<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1206,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[202],"departement-equipe":[2282,214],"specialite-equipe":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-1205","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorie-equipe-personnel-enseignant","departement-equipe-litterature","departement-equipe-francais"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/1205","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1206"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1205"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"categorie-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categorie-equipe?post=1205"},{"taxonomy":"departement-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/departement-equipe?post=1205"},{"taxonomy":"specialite-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/specialite-equipe?post=1205"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=1205"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}